'''第74届奥斯卡颁奖典礼'''是[[美国电影艺术与科学学院|美国电影艺术与科学学院]]旨在奖励[[2001年电影|2001年最优秀电影]]的一场晚会，于[[太平洋时区|太平洋时区]]2002年3月24日在[[美国|美国]][[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]][[好莱坞|好莱坞]]的[[杜比剧院|杜比剧院]]举行，共计颁发了24座奥斯卡金像奖（也称[[学院奖|学院奖]]）。晚会通过[[美国广播公司|ABC]]在[[美国电视|美国]]直播，由劳拉·泽斯金担任[[制片人|制片人]]，路易斯·{{lang|en|J}}·霍维茨导演<ref name="Producer">{{cite news | last = Archerd | first = Army | title = Oscar’s new producer is first femme to solo | url = http://variety.com/2001/tv/news/oscar-s-new-producer-is-first-femme-to-solo-1117852335/ | accessdate = 2014-03-15 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 2001-09-05 | archivedate = 2014-02-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140220225556/http://variety.com/2001/tv/news/oscar-s-new-producer-is-first-femme-to-solo-1117852335/}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Oscar Watch: Horvitz to direct 74th Awards | url = http://variety.com/2002/film/news/oscar-watch-horvitz-to-direct-74th-awards-1117858597/ | accessdate = 2014-03-15 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 2002-01-15 | archivedate = 2014-01-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140116151306/http://variety.com/2002/film/news/oscar-watch-horvitz-to-direct-74th-awards-1117858597/}}</ref>，[[女演员|女演员]][[乌比·戈德堡|乌比·戈德堡]]第四度担任[[主持人|主持人]]<ref>{{cite news | archivedate = 2014-02-21 | url = http://variety.com/2002/film/awards/goldberg-returns-to-host-oscars-1117858062/ | title = Whoopi Goldberg Will Host Oscar Ceremony | last = Archerd | first = Army | work = Vareity | publisher = PMC | date = 2002-01-10 | accessdate = 2014-03-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140221174739/http://variety.com/2002/film/awards/goldberg-returns-to-host-oscars-1117858062/}}</ref>，她之前还曾主持过1994年举行的[[第66届奥斯卡金像奖|第66届颁奖典礼]]、1996年举行的[[第68届奥斯卡金像奖|第68届颁奖典礼]]和1999年举行的[[第71届奥斯卡金像奖|第71届颁奖典礼]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Susman |first=Gary |title=Big Whoopi |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,191444,00.html |accessdate=2014-03-15 |work=Entertainment Weekly |publisher=TimeWarner |date=2002-01-10 |archivedate=2014-01-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140115185103/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C191444%2C00.html }}</ref>。三个[[星期|星期]]前的3月2日，另一位女演员[[查理兹·塞隆|查理兹·塞隆]]在[[比佛利山_(加利福尼亞州)|比佛利山]]的[[比佛利山威尔希尔酒店|威尔希尔丽晶酒店]]主持颁发了[[奥斯卡科技成果奖|奥斯卡科技成果奖]]<ref>{{cite news | last = Horwitch | first = Laura | title = Oscar Watch: Charlize Theron | url = http://variety.com/2002/film/news/oscar-watch-charlize-theron-1117861158/ | accessdate = 2014-03-15 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 2002-02-21 | archivedate = 2014-01-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140112072711/http://variety.com/2002/film/news/oscar-watch-charlize-theron-1117861158/}}</ref>。

《[[美丽心灵|美丽心灵]]》赢得包括[[奥斯卡最佳影片奖|最佳影片]]和[[奥斯卡最佳导演奖|导演]]在内的四项大奖<ref name="LA Times Oscar">{{cite news | last = Welkos | first = Robert | last2 = King | first2 = Susan | title = 'Beautiful' Historic Night | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2002/mar/25/entertainment/et-oscars25 | accessdate = 2014-03-15 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Tribune Company | date = 2002-03-25 | archivedate = 2014-01-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140116143618/http://articles.latimes.com/2002/mar/25/entertainment/et-oscars25}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Lyman | first = Rick | title = 'Beautiful Mind' Wins; Best Actress Goes to Halle Berry | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140128224705/http://www.nytimes.com/2002/03/25/movies/beautiful-mind-wins-best-actress-goes-to-halle-berry.html?pagewanted=all&src=pm | archivedate = 2014-01-28 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2002/03/25/movies/beautiful-mind-wins-best-actress-goes-to-halle-berry.html?pagewanted=all&src=pm | accessdate = 2014-03-15 | work = The New York Times | publisher = The New York Times Company | date = 2002-03-25}}</ref>。其它获奖电影包括同样获奖四项的《[[指环王：护戒使者|指环王：护戒使者]]》，获奖两项的《[[黑鹰坠落|黑鹰坠落]]》和《[[红磨坊_(电影)|红磨坊]]》，获奖一项的《会计师》（{{lang|en|''The Accountant''}}）、《[[鸟！鸟！鸟！|鸟！鸟！鸟！]]》、《[[高斯福庄园|高斯福庄园]]》、《[[长路将尽_(电影)|长路将尽]]》（{{lang|en|''Iris''}}）、《[[死囚之舞|死囚之舞]]》、《[[怪物公司|怪物公司]]》、《周日早晨谋杀案》（{{lang|en|''Murder on a Sunday Morning''}}）、《[[三不管地帶_(電影)|三不管地帶]]》（{{lang|en|''No Man's Land''}}）、《[[珍珠港_(电影)|珍珠港]]》、《[[怪物史瑞克|怪物史瑞克]]》、《透特》（{{lang|en|''Thoth''}}）和《[[训练日|训练日]]》。虽然本次电视直播时长达到创纪录的4小时23分钟，但还是平均吸引了近42万美国观众收看<ref>{{cite web | first = Bill | last = Gorman | title = Academy Awards Averages 41.3 Million Viewers; Most Since 2005 | archivedate = 2013-11-01 | url = http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2010/03/08/academy-awards-averages-41-3-million-viewers-most-since-2005/44217/ | work = TV by the Numbers | publisher = Tribune Company | date = 2010-03-08 | accessdate = 2014-03-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131101231748/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2010/03/08/academy-awards-averages-41-3-million-viewers-most-since-2005/44217/ | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

